text: Jara tyanni taurata ani injila ani tya dharmasastrance palana kele asate je tyancyakade, tyancya palanakartyatarphe utaravile geleta tara tyanna apalya varunahi ani payakhalunahi bharapura (annasamagri) khayala labhale asate. Tyacyatala eka samuha madhalya margavara ahe, matra adhikansa duracari aheta
